[Still, the list of troubled Drexel bond offerings dwarfs that of any
firm on Wall Street,]150 [as does its successful offerings.]151
[Troubled Drexel-underwritten issues include Resorts International,
Braniff, Integrated Resources, SCI TV, Gillette Holdings, Western
Electric and Southmark.]152

["Quality junk bonds will continue to trade well,"]153 [says Michael
Holland, chairman of Salomon Brothers Asset Management Inc.]154 ["But
the deals]155 [that never should have been brought]156 [have now
